<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/shabana-mahmood> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Shabana Mahmood was appointed Secretary of State for the Home Department on 5 September 2025. She was previously Lord Chancellor and Secretary of State for Justice between 5 July 2024 and 5 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Birmingham Ladywood in July 2024."@en .
